name: Dummy robots
description:
Adventure yourself as a new entrepreneur who well, spent all his budget on a cool warehouse. Now to do his jobs, he has cheap robots that suffers from memory leak. It's up to you to fix them, but for how much time?

This game was realized during the 12th Ubisoft Creative Jam with following infos
